	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/meet-our-alumni-zeke-santamaria" hreflang="en">Meet our alumni - Zeke Santamaria</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2024-11-01T18:06:21-05:00" class="datetime">November 1, 2024</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">Zeke Santamaria is a seasoned DevOps expert with over 20 years of experience in software engineering. His journey in IT began after earning a degree from St. Thomas University in 2009.</p>
	</div>

</div>
    </div>


  


    <div class="feature-article">
          


<div class="field-content">
    <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-thumbnail">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/cse.umn.edu/files/styles/medium/public/lulu_profile2_0.jpeg.webp?itok=ATETlaLf" width="220" height="147" alt="Lulu Wang" class="image-style-medium" />


</div>
      
  </article>
 

	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/meet-our-alumni-lulu-wang" hreflang="en">Meet our alumni - Lulu Wang</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2024-11-01T17:55:53-05:00" class="datetime">November 1, 2024</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">Lulu Wang is an established professional with extensive experience in the tech industry. After earning her BS in Electrical Engineering from St. Cloud State University, she began her career as a software engineer at Nonin Medical, Inc. With over a decade of experience, Lulu currently leads data-driven optimization in modem software at Qualcomm, overseeing cross-functional teams throughout the entire project lifecycle (ML or non-ML), from problem to commercialization. In addition to her technical role, she is also a board member of Qualcomm Employee Networks, where she is dedicated to helping women and emerging leaders advance their careers.</p>
	</div>

</div>
    </div>


  


    <div class="feature-article">
          


<div class="field-content">
    <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-thumbnail">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/cse.umn.edu/files/styles/medium/public/Messenger_creation_374A6F79-6279-41D5-BDD8-14A4250A8CF4_1.jpg.webp?itok=QTlBHHvm" width="220" height="213" alt="Prapti Shrestha Headshot" class="image-style-medium" />


</div>
      
  </article>
 

	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/meet-our-alumni-prapti-shrestha" hreflang="en">Meet our alumni - Prapti Shrestha</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2024-09-23T14:07:23-05:00" class="datetime">September 23, 2024</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">After graduating with a B.Sc. in Computer Science, Bioinformatics from Winona State University in 2010, Prapti Shrestha made the decision to join the MSSE Master’s program in 2012 at the University of Minnesota. This decision came after searching for a software engineering program that would align with her work schedule and future career.</p>
	</div>

</div>
    </div>


  


    <div class="feature-article">
          


<div class="field-content">
    <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-thumbnail">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/cse.umn.edu/files/styles/medium/public/UK_Closeup_1.jpg.webp?itok=klcCe1W-" width="165" height="220" alt="Dr. Udhaya Kumar Dayalan" class="image-style-medium" />


</div>
      
  </article>
 

	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/meet-our-alumni-dr-udhaya-kumar-dayalan" hreflang="en">Meet our alumni - Dr. Udhaya Kumar Dayalan</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2024-03-01T15:01:18-06:00" class="datetime">March 1, 2024</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">The discovery of the MSSE program proved to be transformative. It provided the perfect balance, allowing me to continue working full-time while acquiring practical skills and knowledge crucial for advancement in my field. Tailored for professionals like myself, this program not only enabled me to financially support my family, but also allowed me to invest in my future.</p>
	</div>

</div>
    </div>


  


    <div class="feature-article">
          


<div class="field-content">
    <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-thumbnail">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/cse.umn.edu/files/styles/medium/public/212.JPG.webp?itok=yhxNeHSJ" width="182" height="220" alt="Ryan Ricard Headshot" class="image-style-medium" />


</div>
      
  </article>
 

	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/meet-our-alumni-ryan-ricard" hreflang="en">Meet our alumni - Ryan Ricard</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2023-03-13T23:13:22-05:00" class="datetime">March 13, 2023</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">MSSE was an opportunity to step back from my narrow view of the software world to study the entire end-to-end practice of software engineering. Prior to MSSE, I had over seven years of heads down coding experience but did not yet understand the complete effort involved to orchestrate the creation of world class software systems, from inception to completion. Thanks to MSSE, I am now confident that I can lead nearly any software engineering challenge to a successful outcome.</p>
	</div>

</div>
    </div>


  


    <div class="feature-article">
          


<div class="field-content">
    <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-thumbnail">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/cse.umn.edu/files/styles/medium/public/BradJewell_goldy.jpg.webp?itok=buJFUhc5" width="220" height="147" alt="Alumnus" class="image-style-medium" />


</div>
      
  </article>
 

	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/meet-our-alumni-bradley-jewel" hreflang="en">Meet our alumni - Bradley Jewel</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2023-03-13T23:08:25-05:00" class="datetime">March 13, 2023</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">The skills I learned in the program were put to an abrupt test when I was unexpectedly promoted. If I had been given the promotion before attending the MSSE program, I&#039;m not sure how successful I would have been. Everyday I draw on things my professors have taught me. I&#039;ve been able to avoid numerous missteps thanks to the MSSE program.</p>
	</div>

</div>
    </div>


  


    <div class="feature-article">
          


<div class="field-content">
    <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-thumbnail">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/cse.umn.edu/files/styles/medium/public/DennyCheng%202.jpg.webp?itok=odAfAPB8" width="220" height="220" alt="Denny Cheng" class="image-style-medium" />


</div>
      
  </article>
 

	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/meet-our-alumni-denny-cheng" hreflang="en">Meet our alumni - Denny Cheng</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2023-03-13T23:05:36-05:00" class="datetime">March 13, 2023</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">The program has helped me to become a more well-rounded engineer from a technical and leadership perspective. Before coming into the program, I didn&#039;t have much experience in understanding what was true enterprise software. The MSSE program taught me to think critically and to understand that &quot;it depends&quot; truly is the answer to any technical decision.</p>
	</div>

</div>
    </div>


  


    <div class="feature-article">
          


<div class="field-content">
    <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-thumbnail">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/cse.umn.edu/files/styles/medium/public/C.%20Cumberbatch.jpg.webp?itok=rYUFRRtL" width="220" height="159" alt="Chris Cumberbatch" class="image-style-medium" />


</div>
      
  </article>
 

	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/meet-our-alumni-christopher-marc-cumberbatch" hreflang="en">Meet our alumni - Christopher-Marc Cumberbatch</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2023-03-13T23:00:12-05:00" class="datetime">March 13, 2023</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">One of my work colleagues, who is an alumni of the program, strongly recommended it after learning that I was interested in studying software engineering. My decision was based on the reputation of the University of Minnesota and that I could continue working while I earned my degree.</p>
	</div>

</div>
    </div>


  


    <div class="feature-article">
          


<div class="field-content">
    <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-thumbnail">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/cse.umn.edu/files/styles/medium/public/John%20Kruse.jpg.webp?itok=ygXLbIq-" width="125" height="220" alt="John Kruse" class="image-style-medium" />


</div>
      
  </article>
 

	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/faculty-spotlight-john-kruse" hreflang="en">Faculty Spotlight - John Kruse</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2023-03-09T16:08:48-06:00" class="datetime">March 9, 2023</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">After 36 years of doing AI research/prototyping and usability/human factors for 3M; John Kruse shares his interest in user experience in the classroom with articles, books, and dissecting humans and their interactions with technology. A few things he hopes student will take away from his courses are to consider different perspectives, listen, and aim to create the best experience for users. </p>
	</div>

</div>
    </div>


  


    <div class="feature-article">
          


<div class="field-content">
    <article class="media media--type-image media--view-mode-thumbnail">
  
      
            <div class="field field--name-image field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item">  <img loading="lazy" src="/sites/cse.umn.edu/files/styles/medium/public/Allan%20Tokuda%20Headshot-1_web.jpeg.webp?itok=21o_DAFQ" width="220" height="147" alt="Allan Tokuda Instructor MSSE" class="image-style-medium" />


</div>
      
  </article>
 

	<div class="news-summary">
		
				
		<h2 class="news-title"><a href="/msse/feature-stories/faculty-spotlight-allan-tokuda" hreflang="en">Faculty Spotlight - Allan Tokuda</a></h2>
		<p class="news-date">Posted <time datetime="2023-03-09T16:06:17-06:00" class="datetime">March 9, 2023</time>
</p>
		<p class="news-text">With a background in mechanical engineering, Allan Tokuda has knowledge of both sides, physical and digital, of a product. Tokuda is an MSSE alum himself and believes the program&#039;s masters level allows a space for mutual learning between instructors and student. He encourages is classes to try and apply the concepts to real world situations, while being mindful of where that focus is. </p>
	</div>

</div>
